thread.title_full: R&G Brenner Income Tax reviewed by Titus & Recho

author: Titus & Recho
title: Titus & Recho
text:
The R&G Brenner that I go to on Webster Avenue in The Bronx is efficient, courteous and well organized. Eymee Garcia is an excellent and ultimate professional. She is knowledgeable and down to earth. I have had my taxes prepared there for over a decade and I will continue to use the service.
You won't be disappointed if you, too, try them.
